gmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd73eb70aada6078165c887a0c9904e5c2a4f3dd","tid":252681,"uid":72117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:38:04.000Z","msg":"餓住個底先"},{"pid":"e69acd3c22ebd60dfbfc8307959b691727708767","tid":252681,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當一個人做緊啲野但係好唔專心咁望住你佢就係卧底</blockquote><br />\n咁咪通街都卧底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多架"},{"pid":"7611870ff98aa1ccb2f55fc27c88052c47bec5ba","tid":252681,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:00:25.000Z","msg":"我識得有個中學同學畢業之後加入黑警, 宜家去左水房高佬發個度做卧底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c782e9ded32f612c5f80bf5f8b4c8bc022889b1","tid":252681,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我識得有個中學同學畢業之後加入黑警, 宜家去左水房高佬發個度做卧底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7383f078c4b0252224c57d48c3265d51a854e8b4","tid":252681,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"入到去最後發現大半堆人都係卧底，目標只係得一個，捉大佬賣淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a6d0f8d98ecf8c65a77ce495d1da0925994884","tid":252681,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我識得有個中學同學畢業之後加入黑警, 宜家去左水房高佬發個度做卧底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦 因係走左去做卧底會講你知？<br />\n自己老母都唔撚知呀 <br />\n呢3年黎老豆老母已經當無生過我<br />\n我都無見過佢地3年啦<br />\n訓蘢屋 條女早就分左手啦<br />\n話咩好唔成熟 成日周街浦<br />\n識埋d 唔3唔4既人 仲食埋煙<br />\n你估我想嫁 咪都係搵左攞料<br />\n你地知唔知當全世界都誤會<br />\n你係一個垃圾古惑仔 你有幾難受呀<br />\n唯有有時精神寄託下連登<br />\n係到呻下講下 反正又無人識我"},{"pid":"b3c2d1c8928c33a48e6502d97c069933f853cec4","tid":252681,"uid":87210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我識得有個中學同學畢業之後加入黑警, 宜家去左水房高佬發個度做卧底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦 因係走左去做卧底會講你知？<br />\n自己老母都唔撚知呀 <br />\n呢3年黎老豆老母已經當無生過我<br />\n我都無見過佢地3年啦<br />\n訓蘢屋 條女早就分左手啦<br />\n話咩好唔成熟 成日周街浦<br />\n識埋d 唔3唔4既人 仲食埋煙<br />\n你估我想嫁 咪都係搵左攞料<br />\n你地知唔知當全世界都誤會<br />\n你係一個垃圾古惑仔 你有幾難受呀<br />\n唯有有時精神寄託下連登<br />\n係度呻下講下 反正又無人識我</blockquote><br />\n難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw good luck bro"},{"pid":"0432387ac8d3c6ec614a210d10101943c6362ad7","tid":252681,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:11:59.000Z","msg":"做返休班個時做既野"},{"pid":"cb3990f9995a4a98f6c0b443abc431c38d037eab","tid":252681,"uid":37753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:12:16.000Z","msg":"做番自己就得"},{"pid":"8e87fa6c9604832280794f2609c0055d8a2a72be","tid":252681,"uid":12751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/081120_a9d9e5fb89d37a114619149d064b612b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F081120_a9d9e5fb89d37a114619149d064b612b.jpg&h=d8b051d3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套劉浩龍個角色真心on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係佢大佬重on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces